fields.comments: Attached: WAMTRAM extract for tag WA49138.

Bill Hope <bill@colong.com.au>: photos from 26 May 2010 are other remains, not this turtle. hence this turtle must have died between 26 May 2010 and 1 June 2012. Resighted on same, still very dead turtle 2013.
Bob: Bill's 2012 dated images suggest this tagged female loggerhead turtle may have wandered into that dune field and become lost some time in the preceding 2011 -12 nesting season.
Bob: Turtle was smaller than average size for WA nesting loggerheads

fields.management_actions: Moved by ranger Amanda Gatt above high water mark to prevent it from washing further along the beach. Disposed of by Joondalup Council.
